\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 ## 3. Goals, non-goals & success metrics [CPO]\cf0 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 ### 3.1 Goals (V1)\cf0 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 - \cf0 \strokec4 G1. Give the bank a **portfolio-level command dashboard** (Control Tower) with real KPIs and an attention queue.\cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 - \cf0 \strokec4 G2. Make the **Case the central aggregate** \'97 every action, document, payment, cost, and SLA timer hangs off it, with an immutable timeline.\cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 - \cf0 \strokec4 G3. Deliver a clickable, **role-aware** experience across all five operator roles with server-side scoping.\cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 - \cf0 \strokec4 G4. Prove the seven core user flows **end-to-end**, each writing audit events.\cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 - \cf0 \strokec4 G5. Ship data-quality validation ("**\uc0\u1087 \u1088 \u1072 \u1074 \u1080 \u1083 \u1100 \u1085 \u1086 \u1089 \u1090 \u1100  \u1079 \u1072 \u1087 \u1086 \u1083 \u1085 \u1077 \u1085 \u1080 \u1103  \u1082 \u1072 \u1082  \u1089 \u1077 \u1088 \u1074 \u1080 \u1089 **") at portfolio ingest.\cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 - \cf0 \strokec4 G6. Model the **institutional-identity** principle: cases belong to the bank org, not to an individual's signature.\cb1 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 ### 3.2 Non-goals (explicitly out of scope for V1)\cf0 \cb1 \strokec4 \
