\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 - \cf0 \strokec4 Real e-signature (\uc0\u1069 \u1062 \u1055  / E-IMZO) \'97 modeled as an operational attribute, not a real crypto signature.\cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 - \cf0 \strokec4 Real payment rails.\cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 - \cf0 \strokec4 Native mobile apps (V1 is responsive-to-tablet web).\cb1 \
